    <td align="center" bgcolor="#ececec"><font face="Arial" size="2"><strong>Adios compañero
    Andre Gunder Frank</strong></font><br>
    <font face="Arial" size="1"><strong>Textos:<br>
    <a href="agfobit2.htm">Samir Amin</a> - <a
    href="agfobit1.htm">Miguel A. Bernal</a> - <a
    href="agfobit5.htm">Theotonio Dos Santos</a> -<a
